# Now can authenticate as any user
```

**Remediation**:
1. Generate cryptographically random JWT secret at installation
2. Store in OS-level secure storage
3. Rotate JWT secret periodically
4. Implement token revocation list
5. Use asymmetric keys (RS256) instead of symmetric (HS256)

